Chapter 6, Mindful Distraction.

162
00:15:51,050 --> 00:15:53,290
Imagine standing in the eye of a storm.

163
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:59,930
All around you, chaos reigns, wind howls, debris flies, and the world seems to spin out of control.

164
00:16:00,670 --> 00:16:07,410
